eight: 21.3333px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br></p>\n <p><img src=\"/upload/img/project/0/10010_20170725155613.png\" title=\"10010_20170725155613.png\" alt=\"book.png\"></p> \n</div>','1','1','1',NULL),('14fc6c3d874943e4809906c3b2a1f7c8',NULL,'<h1 class=\"jf-article-title\">憨憨电影—基于jfinal搭建的电影网站</h1>',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'<div class=\"jf-article-content\"> \n <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;本人利用闲余时间，通过jfinal搭建的一个电影网站,里面收录的都是高质量的电影。</p>\n <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;项目的主要架构是 nginx + tomcat + jetty + redis + mysql 。其中，nginx作为静态文件服务和负载均衡；tomcat 和 jetty 作为应用服务器，处理请求；redis取代session；mysql数据库大家都懂。另外，SSL 证书使用的是开源的Let\'s Encrypt。</p>\n <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;欢迎大家访问，网址是<a href=\"https://www.hanhanfilm.com\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hanhanfilm.com</a>&nbsp; <br></p> \n</div>','1','1','1',NULL),('4789514b8c594df6999f0b0687c69fc0',NULL,'<h1 class=\"jf-article-title\">finalcms一款轻量级可定制性插件的cms系统（待完善）</h1>',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'<div class=\"jf-article-content\"> \n <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; white-space: normal;\">本项目基于java极速开发框架&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;\"><a href=\"http://git.oschina.net/jfinal/jfinal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(64, 120, 192); text-decoration: none;\">JFinal</a></span></p>\n <blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px 15px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); border-left-width: 4px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; line-height: 24px; white-space: normal;\">\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">简化业务员代码量，极速的cms框架，java插件热插拔式支持系统工作,可任意定制系统的任意页面，插件只需要编译，界面安装即可使用.和系统插件完全分离</p>\n </blockquote>\n <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; white-space: normal;\">系统核心功能包括<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">1.&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;\">前台主题嵌套</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">2.&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;\">页面样式定制</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">3.&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;\">后台人员权限管理</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">4.&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;\">插件管理</span></p>\n <h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 24px; padding-bottom: 0.3em; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; white-space: normal;\"><a id=\"user-content-项目功能数据库设计图\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"https://github.com/yoqu/finalcms#项目功能数据库设计图\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(64, 120, 192); text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; padding-right: 2px; margin-left: -18px; line-height: 1;\"></a>项目功能数据库设计图</h2>\n <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; white-space: normal;\"><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/yoqu/finalcms/master/docs/pictrues/CMS_Design_picture.png\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(64, 120, 192); text-decoration: none;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/yoqu/finalcms/master/docs/pictrues/CMS_Design_picture.png\" alt=\"design_picure\" style=\"box-sizing: content-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></a></p>\n <h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 24px; padding-bottom: 0.3em; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; white-space: normal;\"><a id=\"user-content-项目简介\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"https://github.com/yoqu/finalcms#项目简介\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(64, 120, 192); text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; padding-right: 2px; margin-left: -18px; line-height: 1;\"></a>项目简介</h2>\n <h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 24px; padding-bottom: 0.3em; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; white-space: normal;\"><a id=\"user-content-如何使用\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"https://github.com/yoqu/finalcms#如何使用\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(64, 120, 192); text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; padding-right: 2px; margin-left: -18px; line-height: 1;\"></a>如何使用</h2>\n <h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; white-space: normal;\"><a id=\"user-content-设置ide\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"https://github.com/yoqu/finalcms#设置ide\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(64, 120, 192); text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; padding-right: 2px; margin-left: -18px; line-height: 1.2;\"></a>设置IDE</h4>\n <ol style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 2em; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; line-height: 24px; white-space: normal;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\">\n  <li><p>下载源代码</p></li>\n  <li><p>使用idea打开项目(项目使用idea 15.05的版本)</p></li>\n  <li><p>主菜单的run选项卡设置&nbsp;<a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/yoqu/finalcms/master/docs/pictrues/menu_editconfiruration.png\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(64, 120, 192); text-decoration: none;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/yoqu/finalcms/master/docs/pictrues/menu_editconfiruration.png\" alt=\"选项卡设置\" style=\"box-sizing: content-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></a></p></li>\n  <li><p>设置标红地方的参数&nbsp;<a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/yoqu/finalcms/master/docs/pictrues/runConfiguration.png\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(64, 120, 192); text-decoration: none;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/yoqu/finalcms/master/docs/pictrues/runConfiguration.png\" alt=\"runConfiguration\" style=\"box-sizing: content-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></a>&gt;启动类为&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;\">org.yoqu.cms.core.config.StartFinalCMS</span></p></li>\n </ol>\n <h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; white-space: normal;\"><a id=\"user-content-导入数据到数据库\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"https://github.com/yoqu/finalcms#导入数据到数据库\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(64, 120, 192); text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; padding-right: 2px; margin-left: -18px; line-height: 1.2;\"></a>导入数据到数据库</h4>\n <ol style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 2em; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; line-height: 24px; white-space: normal;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\">\n  <li><p>项目中docs目录包含finalcms.sql文件，将其导入你的数据库中，数据库使用的是mysql。</p></li>\n  <li><p>在res目录的database_config.txt文件中配置数据库链接信息</p></li>\n </ol>\n <h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; white-space: normal;\"><a id=\"user-content-最后\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"https://github.com/yoqu/finalcms#最后\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(64, 120, 192); text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; padding-right: 2px; margin-left: -18px; line-height: 1.2;\"></a>最后</h4>\n <ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 2em; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; line-height: 24px; white-space: normal;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\">\n  <li><p>快捷键shift + F10运行项目.</p></li>\n  <li><p>浏览器输入localhost即可访问.</p></li>\n </ul>\n <h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 24px; padding-bottom: 0.3em; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; white-space: normal;\"><a id=\"user-content-faq\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"https://github.com/yoqu/finalcms#faq\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(64, 120, 192); text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; padding-right: 2px; margin-left: -18px; line-height: 1;\"></a>FAQ</h2>\n <blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px 15px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); border-left-width: 4px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; line-height: 24px; white-space: normal;\">\n  <ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 2em;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\">\n   <li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;\">问</span>：数据库字段修改如何同步到项目中.</p></li>\n   <li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;\">答</span>：运行核心util包中的ModelGenerator类重新生成（不推荐用户改动系统核心包）</p></li>\n  </ul>\n </blockquote>\n <blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px 15px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); border-left-width: 4px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; line-height: 24px; white-space: normal;\">\n  <ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 2em;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\">\n   <li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;\">问</span>：运行项目显示80端口被占用.</p></li>\n   <li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;\">答</span>：1.关闭占用80端口的应用程序 2.在核心包的config包下StartFinalCMS类中修改START_PORT修改为你想要的启动端口</p></li>\n  </ul>\n </blockquote>\n <h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 24px; padding-bottom: 0.3em; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; white-space: normal;\"><a id=\"user-content-其他\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"https://github.com/yoqu/finalcms#其他\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(64, 120, 192); text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; padding-right: 2px; margin-left: -18px; line-height: 1;\"></a>其他</h2>\n <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; white-space: normal;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/yoqu/finalcms/blob/master/docs/Hook%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3.md\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(64, 120, 192); text-decoration: none;\">Hook文档</a></p>\n <h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 24px; padding-bottom: 0.3em; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; white-space: normal;\"><a id=\"user-content-关于\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"https://github.com/yoqu/finalcms#关于\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(64, 120, 192); text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; padding-right: 2px; margin-left: -18px; line-height: 1;\"></a>关于</h2>\n <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: 0px !important;\">项目发起者:&nbsp;<em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">yoqu</em></p> \n</div>','1','1','1',NULL);

